Setup kit
=========

- make a directory where this kit will be reside(e.g. /var/kits)
- cd KIT_DIR && git clone https://github.com/lego12239/libreoffice-kit.git
- edit libreoffice-kit.REPOS.CONF to replace /var/kits with KIT_DIR
- cp libreoffice-kit.REPOS.CONF /etc/portage/repos.conf/libreoffice-kit

Update kit
==========

- cd KIT_DIR && git pull

Upgrade libreoffice
===============

- emerge -au libreoffice
